-- allow multi-line input
:set +m
-- display type of last expression
:set +t

:set prompt  "\ESC[34m<%s>\n\ESC[1;32mλ=\ESC[0m "
:set prompt2 "\ESC[1;32m |\ESC[0m "

:set editor vim


------ And now, extensions ------
------ …so many extensions ------

